descriptionlist.description: UnlockFX gives you special effects for the unlock animation. Rotate, move, flip, skew your lockscreen while unlocking! UnlockFX includes more than 30 different animations, from simple (one way rotations or directional slides) to complex ones. You can also choose an image to be shown when unlocking. UnlockFX works on iPhone, iPod touch and iPad. Configure options from Settings app
